{"tid":2015132,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解破壞往往比創造簡單？","createTime":"2020-05-13T12:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T00:09:35.000Z","uid":218353,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b522b11f313338f15ba81b9e9931e5afe3b57a","tid":2015132,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"破壞一件藝術品只需一瞬間<br />\n創造一件藝術品甚至要一年<br />\n<br />\n殺一隻豬只係需要一瞬間<br />\n但養大一隻豬可能要幾年<br />\n<br />\n扭斷人嘅關節好簡單<br />\n駁返人嘅關節就好困難<br />\n<br />\n起樓可能要幾年<br />\n拆樓可能只需要幾個鐘<br />\n<br />\n建造人類嘅文明幾多年可能都唔夠<br />\n但破壞人類嘅文明都只係撳一個掣嘅事<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔可以創造比破壞簡單？ 如果得嘅話呢個世界一定進步得好快"},{"pid":"a00ee9f97987d4e8b9e5d2af826bf6509e6d4b9f","tid":2015132,"uid":230791,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"Because entropy always increases in a system"},{"pid":"f13f397084faf73e7391f7e7de2f943743402138","tid":2015132,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"創造一個人只需要10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a26fb65d6686ebc0bb9b06e26414d8bae75422","tid":2015132,"uid":116827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f13f397084faf73e7391f7e7de2f943743402138","tid":2015132,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"創造一個人只需要10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"你既話可能一分鐘"},{"pid":"5bb8769dc01b51602dd1c9c047e6eb604f6eca23","tid":2015132,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13f397084faf73e7391f7e7de2f943743402138","tid":2015132,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"創造一個人只需要10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"h