id":"3df1862db3890d14f5b60b88a8066a68fee3f5ff","tid":2015132,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩又諗到d野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實創造 同破壞<br />\n<br />\n創造就係0至100<br />\n但破壞好多時候 我地都冇計100至0 <br />\n好似你起樓 起樓就0到100<br />\n但拆樓 你要完全係個空間消滅佢都唔客易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}